Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情本王都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于贵国所发生的灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为人民的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王对您感到同情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您,弗雷特公王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:02:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也已经知晓寨巴哈的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此本王也才会紧急赶回都城戈达西姆来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论理由为何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士弃国即为不义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违背君命即为不忠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为弗雷特会需要这种 不忠不义之辈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连他们是为了我们国家,才会如此不顾性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还看穿幻人的伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退了寨巴哈的侦查员…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要进言再等个十年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会因为你的独断,而让这个国家步上灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,有话待会儿再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我的无礼,姊夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我现在已经没有资格,这样喊您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也舍弃了自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王殿下,寨巴哈的侵略已近乎疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎打算将整个盖亚,卷入战乱的漩涡中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧绝不会仅发生于法尼利亚一国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的下一个攻打目标即为弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很遗憾地,父王他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,阿斯顿王打算对此放任不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认为那么做才是真正为阿斯多利亚好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当整个盖亚都落入了寨巴哈手中之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚真的可能独自享有和平吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连·歇萨尔为了阻止此事发生因此只身来到弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王殿下,请您原谅亚连吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既聪明且仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚有位好公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你愿意成为我国兵士与寨巴哈对抗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下性命已交付公王之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王相当期待你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是西特的父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月的少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那名少女能够轻易看出 身披隐形披风的人型装甲位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说还能透过预测命运将龙引导至有利位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想见识那股能够影响 我的命运预测装置的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远回忆的彼方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤□开始在愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在乎阿斯多利亚,还有弗雷特会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你能平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,小瞳有没有来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,她没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我还是会看到呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也还真不腻耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不了解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了,为什么我还是会看到呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦,为什么?为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦死人了,梵大人在找你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,简直是伤痕累累嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王你用剑太粗鲁了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢拉撒特的剑,连半条伤痕也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不像亚连那么会用剑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王在闹脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长他当然也会把剑弄伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没你厉害就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能借用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,我不是要你一同上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够说中未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能够发现隐形的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望你能用那股力量 告诉我寨巴哈会从哪里攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,这点子不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是顺利的话,就能给他们来个下马威
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你就是我们的胜利女神啰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我想得那么好用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在地球上,只是个普通的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜也只是稍微比其他人准确一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…在来到盖亚之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜居然准得让我感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还常常看到一些恐怖的预见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再叫我占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我看到恐怖的预见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳帮我算算我和我男朋友的速配程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,是我先的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候跟他告白比较好,帮我算算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳算得好准喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜明明只能算是一种游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了,无论是占卜还是预见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莲妮生前住过的离宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将她在嫁过来之前 使用过的建筑物整个搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都还是跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还维持原状
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就随你自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做我相信,玛莲妮一定也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要离开了是吗,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莲妮公主,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊,祝您幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡不着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得要是现在睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就没办法再醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我想睡觉时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑里就会浮现出战争的事,让我不停地发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就如同父王所说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不具备成为王者的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法变得像父王一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后也是希望我能成为了不起的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总是说亚连的事迹给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法达成母后及父王的期许
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说都具有不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾听我祖母说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能变成那样 自己要是能那样该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心里一直想着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来梦想就一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想会实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一直想着要变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就会好好努力,好好加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,相反地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老觉得行不通 老想着自己绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的梦想不可能会实现的话 那就真的会没办法成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要强烈地抱持希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天,梦想就会传达到那颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而星星就会助我们 最后的一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星会帮助我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子,我来帮你算算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来替你问问星星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔罗牌占卜就是借助星星的力量来占卜未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来算算你的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄三十四之月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺叶巴王叔带我,一起去参观武术大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他应该是担心我 老是待在房间里才这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我对武术明明就毫无兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚骑士团的年轻天才剑客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玛莲妮王姊的日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧十二之月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发青年被任命为"天空骑士"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚王国中仅十二位 备受载誉的骑士才得以乘其名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是当之无愧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接下了王宫的警备工作而来到帕拉斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对父王撒的娇,看来是生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L'lmperatore（皇帝）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Giustizia（正义）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你会慢慢累积实力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LA Luota（命运之轮）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将会通过某个重大考验…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与弗雷特公王的婚约已成定局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会生于王家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经爱上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是生于王家的女子与骑士的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我明明就如此深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莲妮王姊对亚连…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的,是那晚的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉公王的话,他会说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会扳起手指头细数…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是不可能瞒得了他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神好像没办法集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颠倒的LA lmperatrce（女帝）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁忌之恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说西特是亚连跟玛莲妮王姊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈四魔军好久没全员到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,亚德罗福斯将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您能够成为这次战争的先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰阵形排列完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿神明给予庇护!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青铜军,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑铁军,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银军,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那么多人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王,敌军似乎已于四方布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数约有五万五千人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型装甲超过一万架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想死守城门…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯,你应该很清楚 我们生为弗雷特人的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来执行传承之书"狮子之卷"的日子到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传承之书"狮子之卷"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到城门去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,小瞳就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,请您一定要平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,你们驾驶库鲁杰特飞到城的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶谢拉撒特迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和玛莲妮公主有关,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实曾与玛莲妮公主相爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她与弗雷特公王的婚姻成定局前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,西特王子很可能是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙击队已就定位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时维持原状待命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦攻入城后按照计划行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,军师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家牺牲生命为的只是要让我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血红的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.19,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:05.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.27,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:19.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:26.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.63,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:34.43,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:49.41,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:19.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:21.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:26.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:34.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:49.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


